{"tid":1627849,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"政府射死市民！！血腥星期天","createTime":"2019-10-05T18:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T19:08:22.000Z","uid":241173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6bddbd5920d78c29c7019ae3f212bbee346fedde","tid":1627849,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:19:26.000Z","msg":"唯有上街先有上面既人派人落黎查！<br />\n1972年1月30日，<br />\n市民不滿政府未經審訊拘留，在1月30日遊行，軍人福特發表聲明，定義是非法遊行，進行鎮壓。雙方衝突，形勢嚴峻。溫和派議員意識形勢嚴峻，告誡市民剋制，不可暴力。<br />\n遊行氣氛緊張，年輕人偏離路線，向軍人投擲石塊。政府用射擊，14人死，包括記者，旁觀者，死的人都沒有攜帶武器。<br />\n<br />\n政府調查。第一次調查叫做威傑里法庭，開脫政府和軍人責任，但遭很多批評。<br />\n<br />\n第二次調查於2010年完成，指出死傷者當時不構成威脅，被殺是無辜。因此軍人殺市民不合法！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\nfrom城寨<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d-tb96eByYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd-tb96eByYM&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=d53a57ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d-tb96eByYM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.momovod.com/vod-play-id-106139-src-1-num-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.momovod.com%2Fvod-play-id-106139-src-1-num-1.html&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=9e38f91b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.momovod.com/vod-play-id-106139-src-1-num-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"c480774928fd846037ac66dba04650ca53debaf5","tid":1627849,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:19:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b926741e65e497d839f1844599dc6422c5238034","tid":1627849,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:19:45.000Z","msg":"軍人殺市民不合法"},{"pid":"fb826e163c0b8dee213f41c9571116080cc3c0ab","tid":1627849,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:21:15.000Z","msg":"政府用實彈射擊，14市民死"},{"pid":"b3edb1776baa5a91f54c669757b84738ca742cfa","tid":1627849,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:21:38.000Z","msg":"<span